The dataset used in this work will be found at the following link:

**https://huggingface.co/datasets/bitupandeka/LoomGen**

The dataset consists of traditional Assamese handloom motif images collected
from Sualkuchi, Assam. It is an image-only dataset with no class labels and is
intended for unsupervised generative modeling tasks.

Please refer to the dataset card at the above link for detailed information
regarding dataset structure, licensing, and usage conditions.
